- **Never hard-code CSS values.**  
  Use `theme()` tokens defined in `tailwind.config.ts`.  
- **Spacing scale:** only multiples of `0.5rem` (2 → `p-2`, `mx-4`, …).  
- **Color naming:** use semantic names (`bg-primary/10`, `text-muted-foreground`).  
- **Shadow / radius:** `shadow-sm | shadow-md | shadow-lg`, `rounded-sm | rounded-lg`.  
- **Dark mode:** class strategy. Use `data-[theme=dark]:` utilities for ad-hoc cases.  
- **shadcn components:**  
  - Extend via `className` prop, not by editing generated files.  
  - Re-export customised variants from `/components/ui` to keep imports short.  
- **Animations:** prefer `tailwindcss-animate`; keep keyframes in `tailwind.config.ts` extension.

